msgid "{hwlabel}`BROWSE` (press)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/numark_party_mix.md:14
msgid ""
"Equivalent to double clicking the currently selected item in Library (see "
"{mixxx:coref}`GoToItem<[Library],GoToItem>` control)"
msgstr ""

